{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6147fc7f86","title":"关于撤回驻越南军事总顾问改派武官的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c938cf7ce7","index":0,"year":1956,"month":3,"day":12,"articleId":"6147fc7f86"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"8e403d831d","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长彭德怀1956年3月7日报告的批语。"},{"id":"5d93f612fc","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央书记处书记、国务院副总理。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"f0534f4d3c","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀的报告说：为了逐渐减少我国在越南的军事顾问人员，增派越南军队所需要的技术人员，拟将在越南担任军事总顾问的韦国清撤回，另派一名驻越南武官担任两国的军事联络工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"49541cd4f0","type":"title","text":"关于撤回驻越南军事总顾间改派武官的批语吗","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86"},{"id":"8e403d831d","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、陈、邓阅，退彭，照办。武官人选，要是很好的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86"},{"id":"5d93f612fc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86"},{"id":"f0534f4d3c","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86"}],"page":{"id":"e011ccb154","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"6147fc7f86","start":251,"end":251}}}},"__N_SSG":true}